      "title": "My latest New Scientist cartoon",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/705ddcbaeefb3f4d2c5433f20ae5a352/cdd65c9818cd79d3-3e/s640x960/df51c1cc11016699b2909911cc24a465b291ceeb.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"845\" data-orig-width=\"1200\" alt=\"Title: Bertrand Russell, 1933   Panel 1 Bertrand sits at his desk, puffing on his pipe. He says 'The problem with the world is that fools and fanatics are always so certain of themselves, but wiser people are so full of doubts.'  Panel 2 He gets up and walks over to a mirror.  Panel 3 Pondering his reflection, he muses 'But if I'm certain about this...'   Panel 4 'Does that make ME a fool or fanatic?'   Panel 5 He walks back to his desk. His reflection in the mirror says 'Talking to yourself in a mirror seems pretty doubtful to me.' 'Good point.' says Bertrand. \" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/705ddcbaeefb3f4d2c5433f20ae5a352/cdd65c9818cd79d3-3e/s75x75_c1/d65d7e47e587c74e5752fc976e6f5357c8fb301f.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/705ddcbaeefb3f4d2c5433f20ae5a352/cdd65c9818cd79d3-3e/s100x200/f9bc8629c4127b486d79062e571cf5bbca3c3ea2.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/705ddcbaeefb3f4d2c5433f20ae5a352/cdd65c9818cd79d3-3e/s250x400/81f9ab36989d2b92676d922e9cbf51c5fe7fe5af.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/705ddcbaeefb3f4d2c5433f20ae5a352/cdd65c9818cd79d3-3e/s400x600/f9152a7133fa1b2653b9e3ce86128c22c8a889e9.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/705ddcbaeefb3f4d2c5433f20ae5a352/cdd65c9818cd79d3-3e/s500x750/52be8ec8d8b0a5bb340c0c75056608cb7c240f01.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/705ddcbaeefb3f4d2c5433f20ae5a352/cdd65c9818cd79d3-3e/s540x810/743d908de4b37daf2fc64bc5facd049e6b074461.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/705ddcbaeefb3f4d2c5433f20ae5a352/cdd65c9818cd79d3-3e/s640x960/df51c1cc11016699b2909911cc24a465b291ceeb.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/705ddcbaeefb3f4d2c5433f20ae5a352/cdd65c9818cd79d3-3e/s1280x1920/327a9a467ec3926b029ea2bced3e5ea9795f432b.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"/>"
