      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/034693305bff321e12a409c543ecb05b/01403f8cde819af8-c5/s640x960/37485b087e964f2c794a4f66c8a6807543f3f46c.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"825\" data-orig-width=\"1200\" alt=\"Image:&#10;Night, three medieval men leave a building cluttered with eccentric glassware, contraptions, equipment, books etc, one says to the others &quot;Maybe the real gold was the friendships we made along the way!&quot;&#10;&#10;Caption: Palchemists &#10;&#10;Underneath is the following text: from 'Physics for Cats' by Tom Gauld - order it at www.tomgauld.com\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/034693305bff321e12a409c543ecb05b/01403f8cde819af8-c5/s75x75_c1/82ae8e63a8525ffe378f7944c981a9605c997950.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/034693305bff321e12a409c543ecb05b/01403f8cde819af8-c5/s100x200/1a86cd37ebba3b562f55651620e211d4e3002cd8.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/034693305bff321e12a409c543ecb05b/01403f8cde819af8-c5/s250x400/5dfadc4e117e85ec20feb8997df3e83049858521.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/034693305bff321e12a409c543ecb05b/01403f8cde819af8-c5/s400x600/cc50cc804fe89850542bb5b849825c4d0b276862.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/034693305bff321e12a409c543ecb05b/01403f8cde819af8-c5/s500x750/639be74872dff647ba4d8dc63d7dcdc5b5ff718d.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/034693305bff321e12a409c543ecb05b/01403f8cde819af8-c5/s540x810/4fe73a6ae78d5f4dfb0e248cb440e65d86ec9238.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/034693305bff321e12a409c543ecb05b/01403f8cde819af8-c5/s640x960/37485b087e964f2c794a4f66c8a6807543f3f46c.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/034693305bff321e12a409c543ecb05b/01403f8cde819af8-c5/s1280x1920/763544fa02e3603c223c83654c98df6676031f6b.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"/>"
